<div class='titlecontainer'>
 <h1>Presenting Hargray Definition!</h1>

  <h2>Features</h2>

 <p>
   Hargray Definition allows users to:
 </p>

 <ul>
   <li>Type word into search bar & upon clicking search</li>
   <li>Look up definition of a word & display it to you!</li>
   <li>View the past 5 search terms</li>
 </ul>

 <div class='search-card'>
    <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 mt-5">
        <% if flash[:alert] %>
            <div class="alert alert-warning"><%= flash[:alert] %></div>
        <% end %>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-5" style="width: 400px">
            <%= form_with(url: search_path, method: 'get', local: true) do %>
            <div class="form-group">
                <%= label_tag :word, 'Search term '%>
                <%= text_field_tag :word, nil, placeholder: 'Eg. Perseverance', class: 'form-control' %>
            </div>

            <%= button_tag 'Search', class: 'btn btn-success btn-block' %>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
 </div>
 <br/><br/>

 <div class='definition-card'>
    <h3><%= @definition %></h3>
 </div>

    <p>
        Hargray Communications is a telecommunications provider based out of beautiful Hilton Head Island, South Carolina.    
    </p>
    <p>
    Hargray also supports a variety of technological advancements like high speed internet and media entertainment.
    </p>
 </div>